                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/6568: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-08-30T13:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 30, 1925—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received August 30—3:55 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>363. Consul at Amoy reports today situation quiet, boycott weakening. Presence of
                    United States ship <hi rend="italic">Hart</hi> no longer necessary.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
